description: China United Insurance Service, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides brokerage services related to life insurance, and property and casualty insurance products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers life insurance products, including individual whole life, individual term life, individual health, accidental injury, investment-oriented, foreign currency insurance commodities, travel accident, individual endowment life, and individual annuity insurance. It also provides property and casualty insurance products, such as automobile, casualty, liability, and commercial property insurance. The company markets and sells life, and property and casualty insurance products directly to customers through the sales professionals, who are independent contractors. China United Insurance Service, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Taipei City, Taiwan.
